{"tid":2313525,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"日本影音發燒網站:實測PS5與家庭影院的匹配度，實測比入門級兩萬蚊嘅藍光機質素更佳","createTime":"2020-12-06T00:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T08:08:31.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"997328dc9bbb6fc0802e30fa18a7d8f5e3a6a6bc","tid":2313525,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T00:29:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://av.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/review/review/1291485.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fav.watch.impress.co.jp%2Fdocs%2Freview%2Freview%2F1291485.html&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQo4DkkQuUBcdRTUhzZaMUkok%3D&h=43cb58c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://av.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/review/review/1291485.html</a>  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對PS5的影碟播放能力有這麼個評價:日本市面上雖然有單價兩萬多日元的入門級UHD BD藍光機，但這些機器播放影碟時，其細節的粗糙、影像缺乏立體感、暗部層次混作一團都是可以看到的。PS5仗著自身的硬件和圖形處理能力避免了這一點。  PS5針對多聲道音響系統有調節界面，便於調節各喇叭之間的位置。  天龍/馬蘭士在2020年的新品功放集體支持PS5的4K 120hz/8K輸出，雅馬哈有一部分要靠固件更新。實機測試，不用天龍高端功放，中檔產品4700H的運行就很順利。"},{"pid":"0269351e0a4d2b765eaaa1df912031d18b5bda0b","tid":2313525,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T05:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe3137f4b13fed49d8a18f2249473f6e1ddb73e","tid":2313525,"uid":197222,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T06:24:43.000Z","msg":"依家仲邊有uhd player夠膽冇Dolby Atmos <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a762e8004fa1c7d8b23c3f218b129f72a26095","tid":2313525,"uid":113944,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bfe3137f4b13fed49d8a18f2249473f6e1ddb73e","tid":2313525,"uid":197222,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T06:24:43.000Z","msg":"依家仲邊有uhd player夠膽冇Dolby Atmos <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T06:41:24.000Z","msg":"ps5 support dolby atmos 架<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm